pr_title: Added SSRF detection Module for server log monitoring.
pr_body:
## Status
** READY **

## Description
In this commit i have added a SSRF detection module for the server_log monitoring feature in securetea.
Server log monitoring comes under Log monitoring and already had certain vulnerability modules. Along with that i have added this feature which should be able to log server side request forgery vulnerability attempts.






## Todos
- [x] Tests
- [x] Documentation
- [x] Find Regex for ssrf




## Impacted Areas in Application
List general components of the application that this PR will affect:
All the modifcation and name of files come under  `/lib/log_monitor/server_log`
* utils.py
* detect/ssrf.py
* engine.py
* rules/payloads.ssrf.txt && ips.txt
* rules/regex/ssrf.txt
